ary         = \n | Title           = \n | OriginalTitle   = \n | TranslitTitle   = \n | LineColor       = 03379c\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 6\n | RelDate         = December 10, 2015<ref>{{cite web |url=https://store.kadokawa.co.jp/shop/g/g321509000766/ |script-title=ja:\u9b54\u6cd5\u79d1\u9ad8\u6821\u306e\u512a\u7b49\u751f6 |website=[[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=June 20, 2017 }}</ref>\n | ISBN            =978-4-04-865706-8\n | LicensedRelDate = March 21, 2017<ref name=\"Honor6\">{{cite web| url=http://www.b2c.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/none/the-honor-student-at-magic-high-school-vol-6/9780316466042/?yen | title=The Honor Student at Magic High School, Vol. 6 | website=[[Yen Press]] | accessdate= August 10, 2019}}</ref>\n | LicensedISBN    = 978-0-31-646604-2\n | Summary         = \n | Title           = \n | OriginalTitle   = \n | TranslitTitle   = \n | LineColor       = 03379c\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 7\n | RelDate         = August 10, 2016<ref>{{cite web |url=https://store.kadokawa.co.jp/shop/g/g321603000310/ |script-title=ja:\u9b54\u6cd5\u79d1\u9ad8\u6821\u306e\u512a\u7b49\u751f7 |website=[[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=June 20, 2017 }}</ref>\n | ISBN            =978-4-04-892176-3\n | LicensedRelDate = June 20, 2017<ref name=\"Honor7\">{{cite web| url=http://www.b2c.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/none/the-honor-student-at-magic-high-school-vol-7/9780316471848/?yen | title=The Honor Student at Magic High School, Vol. 7 | website=[[Yen Press]] | accessdate= August 10, 2019}}</ref>\n | LicensedISBN    = 978-0-31-647184-8\n | Summary         = \n | Title           = \n | OriginalTitle   = \n | TranslitTitle   = \n | LineColor       = 03379c\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 8\n | RelDate         = June 9, 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://store.kadokawa.co.jp/shop/g/g321702000435/ |script-title=ja:\u9b54\u6cd5\u79d1\u9ad8\u6821\u306e\u512a\u7b49\